<DATE>11/29/2008</DATE>
<AUTHOR>Jon Yankasky</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>The ride is astounding and the features this car has in unreal. Climate control, all time 4wd, anti lock brakes, tire pressure monitoring system and many others. There is plenty of leg room and head room and the ride is so nice and smooth. I did have the front seats altered. As someone said they were uncomfortable and it is an easy fix. In both seats are three steel rods that can be easily removed and when this is done, the seats are just perfect and comfortable. I also had an upholstery man make a 3 inch pad and add it to the center console and this car is a great comfortable ride. Buy the car/truck. You will not be unhappy. </TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Climate control, 4WD, ride </FAVORITE>
